summary: An ordinance relating to the condemnation proceedings and the laying off, opening, widening and establishing of 15th Avenue West, including grade separations at 15th Avenue W. and W. Emerson Street and 15th Avenue W. and W. Dravus Street, under Ordinance 86751 and making an appropriation from the Seattle General Arterial Improvement Bond 1954 Fund for the payment of certain agreed awards when accepted by the City Council.
